title: Well Get There When We Get There
description:
This week Meredith and Patton play "Would You Rather?", talk about ordering lunch from Postmates at 10:30am in the south, and answer some of your speakpipes. Have something interesting you'd like to share? Email us at HeyDidyouGetMyText@gmail.com, or leave us a voice message at speakpipe.com/didyougetmytext.
